CapDbDump
=========

Capistrano recipes for backing up your database, and transfer database dumps to
your local machine.


Howto
=====

Add these line to your config/deploy.rb file:

$LOAD_PATH.unshift File.dirname(__FILE__) + "/../vendor/plugins"
require "cap_db_dump/lib/cap_db_dump/recipes"

Set the following environment variables properly:

set :database_name,      "" # db name, as defined in database.yml
set :database_username,  "" # db username
set :database_host,      "" # database hostname
set :database_password,  "" # database password
set :ssh_server,         "" # name of the server in your .ssh/config



